---
title: Lauren Conrad's Sweet-As-Honey Chicken with Green Beans over Jasmine Rice
description: From her recipe box to your HelloFresh box, dress up the dinner table with meals from Lauren Conrad’s Capsule Menu. The first recipe is this Sweet-As-Honey Chicken, one of Lauren’s absolute favorites. It’s delectably sticky with bursts of ginger, honey, and soy sauce in the glaze.
